      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "The enterprise RAG golden path pre-selects embedding model, vector store, chunking parameters, retrieval strategy, LLM tier, and auth pattern so teams ship faster with fewer architectural decisions."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Ingestion and query are separated: the ingestion pipeline runs offline to chunk, embed, and index documents; the query service performs hybrid retrieval and calls Claude with a citation-structured prompt."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "ACL filtering happens at the vector store query layer — not in the prompt — ensuring that restricted documents never reach Claude's context window."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "CI enforces retrieval recall ≥ 80 % against a seed eval set before any deployment, preventing regressions in retrieval quality from going undetected."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "Deviations from the golden path are allowed with platform team approval and a benchmark comparison showing the deviation improves the target metric."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
